<title>BANGLADESH: Bangladesh bourses closed for holiday.</title>
<headline>Bangladesh bourses closed for holiday.</headline>
<dateline>DHAKA 1997-04-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>Bangladesh's bourses - the main Dhaka Stock Exchange (DSE) and the Chittagong Stock Exchange - were closed on Monday due to the Bengali New Year holiday.</p>
<p>The DSE all-share price index fell 18.2 points or 1.64 percent at 1,089.09 at the close of Sunday's trading. Friday is weekend in Moslem Bangladesh.</p>
<p>-- Dhaka Newsroom +880-2-506363</p>
